title: For those people who
body:
Call supp in champ select, pick Annie with ignite, start dorans ring and build mejais, ludens and a deathcap and proceed to steal all the ADC's kills

my guess is you actually do want to call mid but forgot how to use a keyboard properly.
here ill teach you   [M]    [ I ]    [D]   press the buttons that look like that in that order, and you should be alright.

you're welcome ^^
